\c 20
\p
\v 1 Waini museki, zvinwiwa zvine simba zvine ruzha; naizvozvo, ani nani anotsauswa mazviri haana kuchenjera.
\p
\v 2 Kutyisa kwamambo kwakaita sekuomba kwehando yeshumba; anomutsamwisa anotadzira mweya wake.
\p
\v 3 Kune rukudzo kumunhu anorega gakava, asi benzi rimwe nerimwe rinokakavara.
\p
\v 4 Nekuda kwechando, simbe hairimi; saka achapemha pakukohwa, asi kusina chinhu.
\p
\v 5 Zano mumoyo wemunhu \add akaita se\add*mvura yakadzika; asi munhu wekunzwisisa achaichera.
\p
\v 6 Ruzhinji rwevanhu rwinodanidzira, umwe neumwe kunaka kwake, asi ndiani achawana munhu wakatendeka?
\p
\v 7 Munhu akarurama, anofamba muzvokwadi yake, vana vake vanomutevera vacharopafadzwa.
\p
\v 8 Mambo, anogara pachigaro chokutonga, anodzinga zvakaipa zvese nameso ake.
\p
\v 9 Ndiani angati: Ndachenesa moyo wangu ndanatswa zvivi zvangu?
\p
\v 10 Zviidzo zvakasiyana, nezviyero zvakasiyana, izvozvo zvese zvinonyangadza Jehovha.
\p
\v 11 Kunyange nomwanakomana anozvizivisa nezvaanoita, kana basa rake rakanaka, kana rakarurama.
\p
\v 12 Nzeve, inonzwa, neziso, rinoona, Jehovha akazviita zvese.
\p
\v 13 Usada hope, kuti urege kuzova murombo; svinudza meso ako, kuti ugogutiswa nezvokudya.
\p
\v 14 Chakaipa, chakaipa! Ndizvo zvinoreva mutengi; asi kana woenda wozvirumbidza.
\p
\v 15 Noridhe ririko, nekorari zhinji; asi miromo yezivo ndicho chinhu chinokosha kwazvo.
\p
\v 16 Mutorerei nguvo yake, iye wakazviita rubatso kumutorwa; ngaave rubatso rwavatorwa.
\p
\v 17 Munhu anoti zvokudya zvenhema zvakanaka, asi pashure muromo wake uchazara nejecha.
\p
\v 18 Mano anobva pakurangana; urwe pfumo wamborairirwa nohuchenjeri.
\p
\v 19 Anofamba ana makuhwa, anobudisa zvakavanda; saka usashamwaridzana nomunhu anoshamisa miromo yake.
\p
\v 20 Anotuka baba vake kana mai vake, mwenje wake uchadzimwa parima rakasviba.
\p
\v 21 Nhaka, yakawanikwa nokukurumidza pakutanga, haingaropafadzwi pakupedzisira.
\p
\v 22 Usati: Ndachatsiva zvakaipa; mirira Jehovha, iye achakuponesa.
\p
\v 23 Zviidzo, zvakasiyana, zvinonyangadza Jehovha; nechiyero chinonyengedzera hachina kunaka.
\p
\v 24 Kufamba komunhu kunobva kuna Jehovha; zvino munhu anganzwisisa sei nzira yake?
\p
\v 25 Musungo kumunhu kupika achiti: Chitsvene! Asina kumborangarira, ndokuzofungisisa ambopika.
\p
\v 26 Mambo akachenjera anozungura, vakaipa, achivapura nomupuro.
\p
\v 27 Mweya womunhu mwenje waJehovha; anonzvera zvese zviri mukati-kati.
\p
\v 28 Rudo nokutendeka zvinochengeta mambo; chigaro chake choushe chinotsigirwa norudo.
\p
\v 29 Majaya anokudzwa nokuda kwesimba rawo; ukomba hwevatana ndiyo misoro yakachena.
\p
\v 30 Kurohwa kunokuvadza kunonatsa zvakaipa; kurohwa kunopinda mukati-kati.
